The Ur-Quan Masters is an open-source port of the space epic Star Control 2,
released in 1992 for MS-DOS and 1994 for the 3DO, and whose source code was
freely released by the creators Paul Reiche III and Fred Ford in 2002.

In uqm, you play as a starship captain who explores solar systems across
the galaxy, mining planets for resources, upgrading and customizing your
starship, meeting quirky alien species, and battling your enemies. Fight
to free humanity and planet Earth from the clutches of the evil Ur-Quan!
